DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.377ft at 06:36\n-2.946ft at 07:12\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Old SSW swell and shorter-period WNW swell combo lingers\, keeping waves i
 n the thigh to waist high zone as standouts see better sets on favorable t
 ides. Mid morning high tide slows the small surf. \n\nLight/variable winds
  in the morning\, due to shift moderate offshore NNW over the afternoon. 
