BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260418T075400
DTEND:20260418T103000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.059ft at 07:54\n-2.951ft at 10:30\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Peaking SSW swell sets up waist-chest-shoulder high surf at well exposed s
 pots\, as top summer breaks hit head high. Spots without the good southerl
 y exposure stay small. Tide push helps first half of the morning\, then ti
 de sensitive breaks are bogged down by the mid day high tide. \n\nLight/va
 riable early morning winds\, turn light SW onshore for the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
